<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 01:52:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>2026 年 NVIDIA GTC 圣何塞精选：AI 突破和会议</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/best-of-nvidia-gtc-san-jose-2026-ai-breakthroughs-sessions</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 01:52:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/best-of-nvidia-gtc-san-jose-2026-ai-breakthroughs-sessions</guid></item><item><title>摘要：新生儿的免疫系统具有独特的耐受无害抗原的能力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/abstract-newborns-immune-systems-are-uniquely-primed-to-tolerate-harmless-antigens</link><description>https://doi.org/10.1172/JCI200062&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/abstract134.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 01:37:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/abstract-newborns-immune-systems-are-uniquely-primed-to-tolerate-harmless-antigens</guid></item><item><title>我们可能最终能够治愈许多不同的自身免疫性疾病</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/we-may-finally-have-a-cure-for-many-different-autoimmune-conditions</link><description>我们的免疫系统永远不会停止针对它们视为威胁的细胞，因此，当流氓免疫细胞错误地攻击我们时，就像它们在自身免疫性疾病中所做的那样，这确实是个坏消息。现有的治疗方法可以抑制这些攻击，但不能阻止它们。但事实证明，一种通过杀死流氓细胞来解决这些疾病原因的新方法取得了巨大成功。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/we-may-finally-have-a-cure-for-many-different-autoimmune-conditions.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 01:22:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/we-may-finally-have-a-cure-for-many-different-autoimmune-conditions</guid></item><item><title>抗体 CR3022 的体内进化扩大了 SARS-CoV-2 变体的交叉中和作用并为泛沙病毒免疫提供信息</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/in-vivo-evolution-of-antibody-cr3022-expands-cross-neutralization-of-sars-cov-2-variants-and-informs-pan-sarbecovirus-immunity</link><description>傅等人。使用表达种系 CR3022 重链的 Ig 人源化小鼠来揭示体细胞超突变如何快速使该抗体类别适应广泛的 sarbecovirus 识别。顺序免疫促进了 CR3022 样的成熟，而结构分析表明，亲和力和广度的增加源于微妙的极性和静电细化。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/in-vivo-evolution-of-antibody-cr3022-expands-cross-neutralization-of-sars-cov-2-variants-and-informs-pan-sarbecovirus-immunity2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 01:07:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/in-vivo-evolution-of-antibody-cr3022-expands-cross-neutralization-of-sars-cov-2-variants-and-informs-pan-sarbecovirus-immunity</guid></item><item><title>用于化学活化量子模拟的参量振荡器的不对称控制</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/asymmetry-control-in-a-parametric-oscillator-for-the-quantum-simulation-of-chemical-activation</link><description>研究人员展示了一种超导量子电路，可以模拟化学反应中的隧道效应，揭示状态转换中意想不到的量子效应。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/asymmetry-control-in-a-parametric-oscillator-for-the-quantum-simulation-of-chemical-activation.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 00:52:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/asymmetry-control-in-a-parametric-oscillator-for-the-quantum-simulation-of-chemical-activation</guid></item><item><title>意识对于现实来说是否比量子物理更基础？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/is-consciousness-more-fundamental-to-reality-than-quantum-physics</link><description>存在的一切都可以自下而上构建的想法长期以来一直在物理学家中占据主导地位。现在，一种以意识体验为中心的新型科学正在建设中，并可能解开宇宙最大的谜团。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/is-consciousness-more-fundamental-to-reality-than-quantum-physics.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 00:37:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/is-consciousness-more-fundamental-to-reality-than-quantum-physics</guid></it